    {
      "bookmarkId": "27050043_5_4340-4399",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "4340-4399",
      "markText": "细胞首先以糖类作为有氧氧化的燃料，机体糖供应相对不足时再消耗脂肪，仅在糖及脂肪均相对不足时蛋白质才作为有氧氧化的底物。",
      "totalCount": 51,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=27050043&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=4340&rangeEnd=4399",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/a49320f0719cc03ba49c17b?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=4340&rangeEnd=4399"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "27050043_8_7984-8038",
      "chapterUid": 8,
      "range": "7984-8038",
      "markText": "肌肉在缩短收缩前先进行拉长收缩，使肌肉被牵拉伸长，这样，在紧接着的缩短收缩时，便可产生更大的力量或输出功率。",
      "totalCount": 26,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=27050043&chapterUid=8&rangeStart=7984&rangeEnd=8038",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/a49320f0719cc03ba49c17b?chapterUid=8&rangeStart=7984&rangeEnd=8038"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "27050043_5_3847-3876",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "3847-3876",
      "markText": "只有糖能够直接在相对缺氧的条件下（不完全氧化）合成ATP。",
      "totalCount": 22,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=27050043&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=3847&rangeEnd=3876",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/a49320f0719cc03ba49c17b?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=3847&rangeEnd=3876"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "27050043_8_13287-13336",
      "chapterUid": 8,
      "range": "13287-13336",
      "markText": "大重量力量训练，使肌纤维面积增大，而线粒体数量增加很少，线粒体容积密度相对降低，有氧能力反而降低。",
      "totalCount": 20,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=27050043&chapterUid=8&rangeStart=13287&rangeEnd=13336",
